data.description:
**Price Reduction**
Country property with custom shop featuring 3 overhead doors with drive through access to backyard. Shop also provides a bathroom with a shower. The attached patio is a nice size, perfect place to sit and enjoy the peaceful evenings.  
Home provides 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a sunroom with an open floor plan.  Kitchen features breakfast nook and easy access to the formal dining room - ideal for entertaining. The storm shelter is conveniently located in the attached 2 car garage.
Amazing yard with beautiful trees and plenty of room for a garden or outdoor activities, all sitting on one acre. The location offers privacy, yet still within a reasonable distance to town amenities. Don't miss your chance to own this beautiful property with endless possibilities.
